textAfterTable: It's still a Chauncey Billups world right now, as he boasts the best plus/minus over the past thirty days at a healthy +193. In fact the only non-Detroit or Dallas player to crack the top ten is LeBron James at #9 with a +106 mark. A fun fact: Erick Dampier seems to have taken the lesson to heart after being sent to the bench, and has now posted a +103 plus/minus and 14-2 game by game won lost record over the last month.
